Fun Bar Karaoke (Fan Ba Karaoke)
Thai crime comedy (1997)

Language: Thai
Subtitles: English

Story:
Pu, a misfit young woman has been dreaming of her dead mother building a house. A fortune-teller who tells her that if the dream continues, her father will die when the house is completed. Her father, a playboy is a karaoke regular. He meets a woman of his fantasy called Yok, a high class lady of the night who belongs to a young Chinese mafia. One of the mafia&amp;#039;s hit man named Noi, who having a crush on Pu, but too shy to ask her out. Noi is a half Thai Caucasian, the product left behind by an American G.I. who had a good time with Thai woman during the Vietnam war. Pu can not stop her dream of the house, while her father relationship with Yok brings him one bad luck after another.

